item.title: Need help making an area not wildy! Please help me!
item.dc:creator: @stormcutter stormcutter
item.description:
@stormcutter wrote:

Open up client.java, with ctrl+f, search for the word “nonwild.” Then a list of coordinates comes up, and using the same format add the coordinates of the area you want to make not wild.
